      <title>法国政府赤字减少，预算困境略有缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/france-s-smaller-state-deficit-gives-some-respite-in-budget-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年，法国核心国家预算赤字将缩小，这为政府在修复公共财政的纷争中继续执政提供了一些帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/france-s-smaller-state-deficit-gives-some-respite-in-budget-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 07:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
